# SUMMARY:
# ✅ UPLOADED (tracked):
#    .ipynb .py .sh .sql .html .md .tex .json .toml .lock
#    .png .gif .jpg .jpeg .svg .c .pyx .pxd .h .hpp .cpp
#    .txt .cfg .ini .yaml .css .js .tsx .template .jinja
#    + student PDFs matching the ! patterns above
#
# ❌ EXCLUDED:
#    datasets .csv .npz .npy .ndjson .ff1pkl .pkl .mat .arff
#    models .pth .pt .ckpt .h5 .sav
#    caches .sqlite .db **/fastf1_cache/ **/f1cache/ **/yf_cache/
#    raw data .bz2 .gz .zip .xz **/raw_data/ **/data/raw/
#    lectures **/Lecture Slides/
#    course docs assignment PDFs, quiz papers, exam info, cheat sheets
#    office docs .pptx .docx .xlsx .numbers
#    system .DS_Store .venv/ __pycache__/ build/
#
# ⚠️  Before pushing, run: git status
#     to review tracked files. Force-add with: git add -f <file>
#     Force-ignore any missed course PDF by adding a rule above.
